Σ = {0,1}
The NFA accepts strings containing at least two 0’s or exactly two 1’s. 
L = {00,000,11,011,01010,…}
If a string in the language does not contain at least two 0’s then it will definitely contain exactly two 1’s. If the string in the language does not contain exactly two 1’s, then it will definitely contain at least two 0’s. The strings may contain at least two 0’s and exactly two 1’s.
